So here what I'm trying is as I

00:14:55.926 --> 00:14:57.826 A:middle
touch this button maybe we show

00:14:57.826 --> 00:14:59.066 A:middle
the piece of toast starting to

00:14:59.066 --> 00:14:59.326 A:middle
appear.

